verbose_text: This study also showed that dietary l-isoleucine supplementation enhanced the mRNA expressions of NF-kappaB, TLR3, RIG-I, MDA5, TRIF, TRAF3, NEMO, TAK1, IRF3, and MAVS in the ileum and/or mesenteric lymph nodes of normal and RV infected piglets, which is consistent with the results of in vitro experiment.
evidence: expressions of NF-kappaB, TLR3, RIG-I, MDA5, TRIF, TRAF3, NEMO, TAK1, IRF3, and MAVS
